articles.author: Angus Watson, Chris Lau
articles.title: Synagogue door set alight and restaurant stormed in latest antisemitic attacks in Australia - CNN
articles.description: A man set the door of a synagogue alight and a group of protesters stormed an Israeli restaurant in Melbourne on Friday night, the latest in a wave of antisemitic attacks in Australian cities.
